* {{a|British}} {{enPR|sōk}}, {{IPA|/səʊk/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|əʊk|lang=en}}
* {{a|US}} {{enPR|sōk}}, {{IPA|/soʊk/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|oʊk|lang=en}}
